5b3e2fac9bd1d9c23d21aac0.en-SA: Apple iPhone 11 Pro. It sports a large 5.8inch OLED, Super Retina XDR display that renders brilliant visuals with lifelike color and detail. It has an incredible screen resolution of 2436 x 1125 pixels and has ample brightness of up to 1200nits, which makes it ideal for watching movies or playing high-end games.

5b3e2fac9bd1d9c23d21aabf.en-SA: This smartphone packs in a top-of-the-line A13 Bionic chip and Neural Engine that work seamlessly to deliver a remarkably powerful performance. It has 4GB RAM that ensures smooth operation when switching between different apps and games, or even between browser tabs. This top-class Apple mobile boasts of a triple 12MP ultra-wide, wide, and telephoto camera that lets you take brilliant pictures in almost any lighting conditions. Also, it features a 12MP TrueDepth front camera with f/2.2 aperture that is ideal for selfies, even in slo-mo mode. This mobile includes a high-capacity battery that will easily give you long hours of use on one single charge.
